Its now sunday, so JP and Dcoburn are free to post. Thanx for being a
good sport, Dcoburn, it makes everyone's life easier. Let me be the
first to welcome both of you back.

Its 3am, so I'm going to bed. Goodnight everyone.

::Havoc::

Havoc frowns, scanners reporting to him that the Iron Fist had picked
up a bot landing in Brazil. He looks to Demolition.

"You're in charge. Make sure looney doesn't go anywhere. I'll check
this new pod out."

Looney, was, of course, reffering to Wolfgang. Havoc walks out of the
room and exits the base, flying off toward the new pod.
